  "text": "Their report highlights the importance of stents with drug delivery capabilities and therefore signals the beginning of the era of \"smart\" stents. An important question unanswered in their study is the gender bias in paclitaxel therapy. It is well established that the chemotherapeutic effect of paclitaxel is mediated through the plasma membrane estrogen receptors [CITATION_1] . It is also widely accepted that this is particularly effective in breast and ovarian neoplasms (3) [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
